30 FILLBOX 200 200 (-200) 0
40 PENCOLOR 'BLUE
50 FILLBOX 200 200 0 0
60 PENCOLOR 'GREEN
70 FILLBOX 200 200 200 0
80 SLEEP 4
90 REPLACECOLOR 'BLUE :ERASERCOLOR
