TO SHRINKSQ :XC :YC :OSIDE :NSIDE
20 ERASERUP SETXY (:XC + (:OSIDE / 2)) (:YC + (:OSIDE / 2))
30 ERASERDOWN DELX (- :OSIDE) DELY (- :OSIDE) DELX :OSIDE DELY :OSIDE
40 MAKE 'OSIDE :OSIDE - 2
45 DELXY -1 (-1)
50 IF :OSIDE > :NSIDE THEN GO 30
END

TO BEAM :LENGTH :WIDTH
